
Usage:
-----

    rosrun plug-and-play [cmd] where [cmd] is any of the below:


info:
-----

    Prints out information about a specific plug and play module. 

check:
----- 

    Checks if the module is loaded, the driver is running, and the computer has a connection to that module

install:
----- 

    Installs the module to the computer and runs it on boot. This also configures it to be used with the robot by passing in the x,y,z coordinates relative to the existing robot

list:
-----

    Lists all installed modules and some details about them
